    <p>Fighting someone with a knife is extremely dangerous and difficult.</p>
</div>

<!--more-->

<hr />

<p>Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.00.12.176.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>BLOIK-STRIKE</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.00.36.592.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>when attacker stab,
you block and simultaneously ,palm strike them in the face</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.00.42.647.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>MONKEY GRIP</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.00.45.834.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>stopping them from stabbing,
you grip attacker’s Wrist so that they can’t lined up for another stab.
And than, you palm strikes.</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.00.53.570.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>GRAB WRVIST</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.01.00.063.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>reach over top of their arm</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.01.03.622.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>reach over top of their arm ,you’re
going to grab your own risk.
control them into of your arms verse</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.01.04.954.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>SHOULDER LOCK</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.01.10.751.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>bend their arm back and try to touch</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.01.13.844.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>Kimura use your leg as well to keep them ,
pinned down and get more leverage</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.01.21.095.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>the struggle the arm starts have been in ,the
other direction transition into</p>

<p><img src="/images/youtube\list\fight\fighttips\streetfight\knife\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground\Knife-Defense-on-the-Ground-00.01.29.763.jpg" alt="" /></p>

